data.description:
Are you looking for the perfect 3/2/2 with a bonus room? Look no further!! This 2 story home, located in Murano of Palm City is incredible.  You walk in to a grand entry way and leads you to the living room accented by a shiplap wall. As you move through the home you will be dazzled by the size of the dining/living area located by the huge kitchen. This kitchen, complete with pantry, has cabinets for all of your storage needs. There is a flex room that could be used as a dining area, gym, home office or even a bedroom. There is a half bath (can be converted to a full) on this level as well.  Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms. The primary suite is complete with a walk-in closet and large bathroom with a separate tub/shower. Laundry is located upstairs for occupants ease. Two guest rooms are joined by a jack and Jill bathroom and 1 of the rooms has a large walk in closet as well.


The downstairs wood tile gives this home a luxurious look and feel. The upstairs LVP flooring continues the look and offers comfort on ones feet.  You really will feel like royalty when you can call this place HOME!

You have to come and check this home out!
